=The school in figures=
----

In the School there are 4500 students enrolled in the different degrees. More than 300 are foreign students in exchange programs.
The Human Resources of the School are based on a multidisciplinary work team consisting of professors and researchers (313) and administrative and personnel staff (155). A total of 789 researchers and scholars associated with research projects in departments and laboratories are part of this comprehensive organisation.

*4.500 Students
*300 Foreing students in exchange programs
*More than 300 students from the School studying abroad
*313 Professors

